{
  "description": "A wide shot captures a vast field of dry, golden grass extending towards a distant cityscape and a large container ship. The grass dominates the foreground, its texture suggesting late summer or autumn. A simple wire fence runs along the edge of the field. In the midground, a body of water separates the field from a cityscape featuring buildings and infrastructure, including what appears to be port facilities. A large, red and white container ship is prominently positioned on the water, in front of the city. Beyond the city, hazy hills or mountains rise in the distance. The sky is overcast, creating a soft, diffused light across the scene.",
